WEBVTT

00:01.976 --> 00:03.096
Previously on The O.C.:

00:03.176 --> 00:04.776
Rebecca is gone.
What did you say to her?

00:04.856 --> 00:06.696
I asked her if she was
in love with you,

00:06.696 --> 00:07.856
and she said she was.

00:07.856 --> 00:09.976
I tried to tell Summer, and I couldn't.

00:10.056 --> 00:11.576
So you're here to break up with me?

00:11.576 --> 00:12.456
Then I told her.

00:12.456 --> 00:14.896
I just believe in
taking every precaution.

00:14.896 --> 00:16.616
Caleb is gonna ask for a DNA test.

00:16.616 --> 00:18.776
- You can't let him adopt you.
- What are you talking about?

00:18.776 --> 00:20.416
He might not be your dad.

00:20.416 --> 00:23.576
When we were about to...
there was this voice in my head.

00:23.576 --> 00:24.496
Seth?

00:24.496 --> 00:28.536
Have a great time in Italy.
I'm cool with it. I'm over you.

00:35.656 --> 00:39.976
<i>Well, I cannot believe I'm saying this,
but it's raining in the O.C.</i>

00:40.096 --> 00:44.376
<i>I know, it's crazy. I got to tell you, the
traffic is a nightmare. The 405 is jammed.</i>

00:44.376 --> 00:46.376
<i>The 5, the 710,
they're all gridlocked.</i>

00:46.496 --> 00:49.656
<i>Stay safe, stay dry, and let's all pray
for sunshine again.</i>

